        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Two-person team with payment technology innovation. Strong backgrounds in financial services. Copenhagen fintech scene is target market.</p>
        <p class="text-green-700 font-medium">✓ Approved—clear innovation in payment processing, scalable model, relevant to Danish fintech ecosystem. Now based in Copenhagen, part of Copenhagen Fintech accelerator. Raised Danish VC funding.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Restaurant Owner from Thailand</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">10 years restaurant experience. Wants to open authentic Thai restaurant in Copenhagen. Traditional business model.</p>
        <p class="text-red-700 font-medium">✗ Rejected—restaurants are explicitly listed as typically rejected. Not considered innovative or scalable. Advised to explore other visa routes or countries with less restrictive requirements.</p>
      </div>

